<doc id="594652" wikidata="Q7863571" url="?curid=594652" title="U15 (Berlin U-Bahn)">
<text>The U15 was a line on the Berlin U-Bahn. Originally the U3 running between Wittenbergplatz and Uhlandstraße, it became a branch of the U1 in 1993 as part of the reorganisation of the network following the reopening of the U2.

On December 12, 2004, it was renumbered as the U1.

